om/horse-racing/articles/95225/cannock-chase-takes-canadian-international |work=  |publisher= [[Blood-Horse|Blood-Horse]] |date= 2015-10-18 |accessdate= 2015-12-04 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208092918/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/95225/cannock-chase-takes-canadian-international |dead-url= no }}</ref>。以處女馬身份贏出維多利亞打吡的加官進爵，四歲時贏出一級賽東寶錦標<ref>{{cite news |first= Rod |last= Nicholson |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Chris Waller’s Preferment puts himself in serious contention for VRC Derby-Melbourne Cup double |url= http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/superracing/vic-racing/turnbull-stakes-2015-chris-wallers-preferment-puts-himself-in-serious-contention-for-vrc-derbymelbourne-cup-double/news-story/d65584f2c344b51b1b4ea18abb5b7a26 |work= |publisher= [[先驅太陽報|先驅太陽報]] |date=2015-10-04 |accessdate=2015-12-04 }} </ref>。喜蓮巨星在5月尾險勝[[香港冠軍暨遮打盃|香港冠軍暨遮打盃]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-05/news_2015053101805.html |title=「喜蓮巨星」攻下渣打冠軍暨遮打盃 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |accessdate=2015-12-04 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208100014/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2015-05%2Fnews_2015053101805.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年前冠軍多名利，仍然一直未勝，並遠征澳洲一試實力。喜蓮歡星曾經在5月贏出三級賽[[皇太后紀念盃|皇太后紀念盃]]，其後亦在同程的[[香港冠軍暨遮打盃|香港冠軍暨遮打盃]]屈居季軍。活力歡騰曾經在3月勝出精英碟，其後亦在[[香港冠軍暨遮打盃|香港冠軍暨遮打盃]]跑入第五名。桃花心在去年此賽事跑獲一席季軍<ref name="HKV2014" />。安荃在香港三捷中長途賽事，並在[[婦女銀袋賽|婦女銀袋賽]]跑入季軍。高地之舞表現穩定，並贏出一級賽秘書長錦標<ref>{{cite news |first= Claire |last= Novak |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Highland Reel Brilliant in Secretariat |url= http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/93712/highland-reel-brilliant-in-secretariat |work=  |publisher= [[Blood-Horse|Blood-Horse]] |date= 2015-08-15 |accessdate= 2015-12-04 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208093124/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/93712/highland-reel-brilliant-in-secretariat |dead-url= no }}</ref>。明朝盛世在10月贏出巴黎市議會錦標<ref>{{cite news |first= Scott |last= Burton |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Dynasty back to best with Group 2 success |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/ming-dynasty-france-dynasty-back-to-best-with-group-2-success/1974283/#newsArchiveTabs=last7DaysNews |work=  |publisher= [[Racing_Post|Racing Post]] |date= 2015-10-18 |accessdate= 2015-12-04 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208102431/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/ming-dynasty-france-dynasty-back-to-best-with-group-2-success/1974283/#newsArchiveTabs=last7DaysNews |dead-url= no }}</ref>。大利盈的母系是[[2009年香港國際賽事#香港瓶|2009年香港瓶]]冠軍[[大利來|大利來]]，力圖母子制霸。

