大運財在今年角逐[[主席短途獎|主席短途獎]]中險勝[[友瑩格|友瑩格]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-02/news_2015021501718.html&b_cid=EWRNRNC |title=蘇銘倫夥拍「大運財」勇奪主席短途獎 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |date=2015-02-15 |accessdate=2015-12-04 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208161610/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2015-02%2Fnews_2015021501718.html&b_cid=EWRNRNC |dead-url=no }}</ref>，正式轉為向短途發展。獨掌全權第四度角逐此賽事，今年贏出[[阿喬斯短途錦標|阿喬斯短途錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Sole Power grabs glory at Meydan |url=http://www.irishracing.com/news?prid=121266&;headline=Sole-Power-grabs-glory-at-Meydan |work= |publisher=Irish Racing |date=2015-03-28 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072217/http://www.irishracing.com/news?prid=121266&;headline=Sole-Power-grabs-glory-at-Meydan |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[五利高股錦標|五利高股錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Neil |last= Corlin |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Sole Power leads way for Flying Five |url= http://www.herald.ie/sport/horse-racing/sole-power-leads-way-for-flying-five-31512112.html |work=  |publisher= herald.ie |date= 2015-09-09 |accessdate= 2015-12-05 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208054213/http://www.herald.ie/sport/horse-racing/sole-power-leads-way-for-flying-five-31512112.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。天久今年在KrisFlyer國際短途錦標跑第三。誰可拼曾在4月尾贏出[[短途錦標|短途錦標]]。覓奇島去年贏出NHK一哩盃，今年在短途賽有不錯表現。幸福指數贏出[[百週年紀念短途盃|百週年紀念短途盃]]，去年曾贏出1200米的馬會短途錦標。好好計去年不斷遠征，在美國取得不錯成績。一寶曾於去年贏出香港二級賽短途錦標。翠面棕駿在兩場一級賽跑獲季軍。蒙古周末贏出育馬者盃草地短途大賽，練馬師來自蒙古<ref>{{cite news |first= Mike |last= Welsch |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Mongolian Saturday by a neck in Breeders' Cup Turf Sprint |url= http://www.drf.com/news/mongolian-saturday-neck-breeders-cup-turf-sprint |work=  |publisher= [[Daily_Racing_Form|Daily Racing Form]] |date= 2015-10-31 |accessda