步步友在香港賽事表現出色，贏出多項重要賽事，並成為[[香港馬王|香港馬王]]<ref name="HKHOTY">{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-07/news_2015071002243.html |title=「步步友」榮膺香港馬王 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |date=2015-07-12 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924030854/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2015-07%2Fnews_2015071002243.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在馬會一哩錦標因不利情況下敗陣跑第三。滿樂時贏出兩場一哩一級賽，分別是[[安田紀念賽|安田紀念賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first=章利 |last=柴田 |authorlink= |coauthors= |script-title=ja:【安田記念】新怪物！モーリス４連勝でイッキ戴冠 |url=http://race.sanspo.com/keiba/news/20150608/ope15060805070005-n1.html |work= |publisher=[[產經體育|產經體育]] |date=2015-06-07 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dY0PygI1?url=http://race.sanspo.com/keiba/news/20150608/ope15060805070005-n3.html |archivedate=2015-12-05 |deadurl=yes |title={title} }}</ref>及[[一哩冠軍賽|一哩冠軍賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |script-title=ja:【マイルＣＳ】久々克服！モーリスが春秋マイル王 |url=http://race.sanspo.com/keiba/news/20151122/ope15112215450007-n1.html |work= |publisher=[[產經體育|產經體育]] |date=2015-11-22 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dY0eY4hn?url=http://race.sanspo.com/keiba/news/20151122/ope15112215450007-n1.html |archivedate=2015-12-05 |deadurl=yes |title={title} }}</ref>，美麗之星在冠軍一哩賽前因傷退下火線，復出後在馬會一哩錦標爆出37倍冷門。托摩亞在土耳其贏出二級賽托卡比錦標等兩項二級賽。引以為榮雖未曾勝出分級賽，但屢次在大賽中上名，連續兩度在一哩冠軍賽跑入第二<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |script-title=ja:フィエロは２年連続の２着／マイルＣＳ |url=http://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&year=2015&month=11&day=22&id=1569785 |work= |publisher=[[日刊體育|日刊體育]] |date=2015-11-22 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208041533/http://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&year=2015&month=11&day=22&id=1569785 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。詠彩繽紛是2014-15年馬季[[冠軍人馬獎|最大進步馬匹]]<ref name="HKHOTY"/>，今季一舉攻下[[慶典盃|慶典盃]]及[[沙田錦標|沙田錦標]]。駿馬名駒於2015元旦賽日贏出[[華商會挑戰盃|華商會挑戰盃]]。紅運杜拜在意大利勝出一級賽維托里奧卡普阿錦標。大印銀紙在慶典盃跑獲第二。醒目名駒為2015年香港打吡大賽季軍，今季曾在婦女銀袋賽拼入亞軍，上仗角逐田草二班千八米一放到底。風花雪月在6月贏出精英盃。野田金駒兩歲時贏出[[朝日盃未來錦標|朝日盃未來錦標]]，今年在三級賽富士錦標取勝。賽事唯一雌馬重大機密，則贏一級賽[[羅斯齊爾德錦標|羅斯齊爾德錦標]]以及[[傑克莫華大賽|傑克莫華大賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Andrew |last= Dietz |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Esoterique leads home Fabre one-two in Marois |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/a-fabre-baron-edouard-de-rothschild-pierre-charles-boudot-deauville-france-esoterique-leads-home-fabre-one-two-in-marois/1936046/latest/#newsArchiveTabs=last7DaysNews |work=  |publisher= [[Racing_Post|Racing Post]] |date= 2015-08-16 |accessdate= 2015-12-05 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208162940/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/a-fabre-baron-edouard-de-rothschild-pierre-charles-boudot-deauville-france-esoterique-leads-home-fabre-one-two-in-marois/1936046/latest/#newsArchiveTabs=last7DaysNews |archivedate= 2015-12-08 }}</ref>。

